item.title: IoT Expansion Card PCB CAD/brd files
item.dc:creator: mikebrearton
item.description:
Hi folks, I also am looking for template PCB design files for IoT expansion card; something simple I can take and extend into something useful. The breadboard for example. Something I could then send off to PcbCart (or similar) for production. I currently use DesignSpark, but I’m sure we could find a way to process whatever format you’ve got.
